{
  "texts": [
    "Relationship determination.",
    "MatKG is constructed by merging rows that share identical DOIs.",
    "Specifically, consider two entities, E1 and E2, that are found under the same DOI, termed as DOI-1.",
    "If the database houses the triples [E1, Tag1, DOI-1] and [E2, Tag2, DOI-1], then a novel triple [E1, rel, E2] is created.",
    "In this context, rel is defined as Tag1-Tag2, and a co-occurrence frequency v is assigned to this triple, where v is the number of DOIs containing both E1 and E2."
  ]
}